title: Germany is fed up with the globalist Uber-moron Angela Merkel, who created an enormous magnet to invasion | Obama Birthplace Controversy
text:
(Before It's News) Wall Street Journal
Political Backlash Against Merkel Grows Over Refugee Crisis Wall Street Journal – ‎4 hours ago‎ BERLIN—Political backlash against German chancellor Angela Merkel intensified on Friday as her most conservative ally threatened to take the government to court if it doesn’t adopt measures to limit the flow of migrants into Germany. Merkel Threatened by Bavarian Leader Seeking Halt to Refugees Bloomberg German right-wing party accuses Merkel of ‘people smuggling’ Reuters From Germany: Massive increase in attacks on refugee shelters Deutsche Welle
